snippet.title: KetoCon 2017 Amber O'Hearn The Carnivorous Human
snippet.description:
Update 2018-09-10: Comments are now closed.
Please direct discussion to Twitter @KetoCarnivore
If you have general questions about carnivore diets, please see my starting guide: http://www.empiri.ca/p/eat-meat-not-too-little-mostly-fat.html

Please note: harassment in comments will be flagged and removed.  I may give a pointer to resources if someone asks respectfully, but I am not here to explain in depth why vegan "science" is flawed, or to respond to interrogation.
